narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: A class on books and learning how to write. I would definitely recommend it because it really was a blast plus its a writing credit. I love fiction.
An interesting survey course that offers a wide range of texts as an introduction to world literature. An easy writing credit, too.
A good survey course, helpful to see if you're interested in being a literature major.
